      exception thrown on access to a service that could not be found or is not run by the node which has been asked for it
      class  NoSuchServiceMethodException
      exception thrown on a service method invocation, if the requested method is not implemented at the given service
      class  NotFinishedException
      Exception thrown on access to a result of a L2pThread, when the job is not done yet
      class  ServiceInvocationException
      a Service InvocationException is thrown when the invocation of a service method leads to an internal exception
      class  UnlockNeededException
      Exception thrown in a global invocation, if the remote service tries to open an envelope and is not able to do this, because the private key of the executing agent is not unlocked.
